sets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57536bbd4494413280c23cda23a75f11dd4392e","tid":2489637,"uid":33263,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:17:53.000Z","msg":"一定要判法官死刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4186c9b0aff768915e0cee7c6e15dbed0120b7f","tid":2489637,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc9304507a254706ed6ac7d2392873ab9a1d7f57","tid":2489637,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:09:59.000Z","msg":"網民前年11月13日發起全港三罷，兩名青年早前被裁定在大埔參與非法集結及違反蒙面法等五罪罪成，案件今早判刑。<strong><span class=\"red\">裁判官陳炳宙指案發時17歲的無業青年否認犯案，自辯時更在庭上胡說八道，誣告警員制服他時使用過份武力，可見他沒真誠反省，形容他是「讀書唔成，又冇半點一技之長嘅年輕人」，故拒絕接納報告建議判處青年入住刑期較短的勞教中心，而是將青年判入教導所。至於同案倉務員，陳官指他辯稱受社會氣氛影響而犯案並非求情理由，否則是「全球司法歷史上最大笑話」，最後判他入獄21個月。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210415/ANCSPQELLZC4NHNRBJ5WLQ33KU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210415%2FANCSPQELLZC4NHNRBJ5WLQ33KU%2F&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sJWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=decd6a52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210415%2FANCSPQELLZC4NHNRBJ5WLQ33KU%2F&h=df3e2da7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210415/ANCSPQELLZC4NHNRBJ5WLQ33KU/</a>"},{"pid":"68807110655a296fcdb2337d235f1edf1f30ac65","tid":2489637,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:11:22.000Z","msg":"辯方強調，蘇還柙候判期間明白到案件嚴重性，亦自知令家人傷心失望，冀法庭接納報告建議，判他入勞教中心。惟陳官指勞教中心的刑期太短，不足以反映案情嚴重性，而報告指判入教導所亦適合，認為教導所的刑期較能反映案情嚴重性。<br />\n<br />\n辯方則指，蘇已真誠悔過，勞教中心對體能要求高、相對辛苦，絕非輕判選項。惟陳官反駁稱，蘇從西廚學院輟學，令學習半途而廢，相信他可在教導所再學一門手藝，出獄後重回正軌。<br />\n<br />\n辯方不同意「半途而廢」的說法，強調蘇是因本案而輟學。陳官聞言質疑謂：「咁件案未完結，佢又日日食飯、日日瞓覺，一樣咁做人？」辯方回應稱，若案件尚未完結，蘇的生活便難以如常。<br />\n<br />\n陳官判刑指，高等法院的案例指出，市民行使集會的權利，必須以干擾公眾秩序之行為劃界，否則社會將變得無法無天。案發時正值本港史無前例的社會運動，當天有人發動「全港大三罷」，大埔太和路現場有逾100人非法集結，可見必定有預謀。"},{"pid":"3ff70529ec2c8edb61a7869c95d81ee16163bcda","tid":2489637,"uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:13:23.000Z","msg":"陳炳宙反問求情老師：點解自己學生會相信犯法係追求公義嘅手法？<br />\n<br />\n陳官指，雖然蘇求情稱將會繼續學業，但這不代表他不需面對法律制裁。對於蘇的老師求情指，他因追求公義而犯案，陳官反問謂：「呢位老師應該問一問自己，點解自己學生會相信犯法係追求公義嘅手法？」<br />\n<br />\n對於傳道人求情指，蘇希望透過廚藝為人帶來幸福，陳官則直指：「相信少咗佢呢名中途輟學嘅學廚，唔會令市民少咗幸福。」<br />\n<br />\n陳官亦不相信蘇已反省，稱他在求情信中指不知涉案集結是犯法，反映其所謂「反省」並沒半點真誠。陳官亦不接納蘇年少無知的說法，稱他當時看見警員便欲逃走的舉動，反映他必定自知犯法。<br />\n<br />\n陳官直言，在蘇否認所有控罪的一刻，他已放棄所有獲輕判的機會；但對於初犯的年輕人，判監是最後選擇。懲教主任在報告中僅簡單解釋，因蘇在獄中表現良好，故建議判他入勞教中心。但陳官認為，蘇不但否認犯案，出庭自辯時更在庭上胡說八道，又誣告警員使用非法武力。雖然他聲稱有所反省，卻沒向警員道歉。而他聲稱熱愛廚藝，學廚時卻又半途而廢。<br />\n<br />\n陳官形容，蘇作為一名「讀書唔成，又冇半點一技之長嘅年輕人」，相信比起着重體力懲罰的勞教中心，他更適合在教導所培養守法意識及謀生技能，遂判他入教導所。"},{"pid":"3c0a992cba159a6c15c4d4732e5fc87f9d0b5082","tid":2489637,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:15:10.000Z","msg":"至於巢，陳官指雖然他案發時沒使用暴力，但這不可用作減刑理由，因為若果他有使用暴力，早已被控暴動等嚴重罪行。<br />\n<br />\n對於巢的母親指，他因受社會氣氛影響而犯案，陳官認為守法是個人選擇，巢選擇犯法，就要付出代價，而正正是他這樣的人，才會影響社會氣氛。陳官更直言，若因這個求情理由而獲輕判，「實在係全球司法歷史上最大笑話」。<br />\n<br />\n就非法集結及蒙面罪，巢分別被判監15個月及4個月，全數同期執行；非法管有彈藥罪則判監9個月，當中6個月須與前兩項控罪分期執行，最終總刑期為21個月。<br />\n<br />\n辯方為巢申請保釋，以等候上訴定罪的結果。但陳官認為上訴沒有合理成功機會，故拒絕申請。"},{"pid":"f580dd93871cc28863aedb51c0dfde81e78eacb6","tid":2489637,"uid":77755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:16:20.000Z","msg":"屌你老母狗官咁撚搶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88590aa98595c5a47e125fba9b96b123aee73d0b","tid":2489637,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:19:19.000Z","msg":"cls 紅官"},{"pid":"c05e3c55a83d09739f0245866255df98c4d9f086","tid":2489637,"uid":210233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:19:31.000Z","msg":"雖然老炳寸過馬撚,但教導所好過勞教既。勞教是地獄。而被判入獄有還押扺消,希望不會坐得耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8834d080a142d9bd5090ad1656eb3cae9903fa5","tid":2489637,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:20:23.000Z","msg":"點解粉嶺可以同時出到佢同蘇文隆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad52df48f93789420d22c19c1faa4c69123a04c","tid":2489637,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:20:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15037&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sJWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=96a2ed81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15037</a><br />\n<br />\n= = = = = =<br />\n@15:10 後補資料<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1) D1 &amp; D2 參與非法集結<br />\n(2) D1 在身處非法集結時使用蒙面物品<br />\n(3) D1 管有適合作非法用途的工具並意圖作非法用途使用<br />\n(4) D2在身處非法集結時使用蒙面物品<br />\n(5) D2 無牌管有彈藥<br />\n<br />\n裁決：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14696\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14696&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sJWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=889ef29b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14696</a><br />\n<br />\n10:03 開庭<br />\n裁判官詢問兩名被告有否求情<br />\n<br />\nD1轉咗由黃大律師代表求情，解釋咗懲教署嘅報告畀被告聽，對內容不爭議，案發時被告17歲，無刑事紀錄，就謮西廚學院，舊年停學有做part time ，希望事件完咗之後再入謮西廚學院，呈上多封求情信，有青少年社工服務處社工，中學蘇老師，被告大家姐，被告母親，和被告自己，表示後悔，在還押期間，知道行為嚴重，令家人傷心失望；懲教署報告認為勞教中心和教導所兩者都可以，建議比較適合入勞教中心，但裁判官表示在上次判刑時，已經聲明在先不一定考慮勞教中心，勞教時太短，不足以反映案情嚴重性，裁判官話要考慮被告嘅福祉，教導所學一門手藝，對社會有益處。<br />\n<br />\nD2無進一步求情，官需要時間考慮判刑，11:00再訊。<br />\n<br />\n11:15 開庭<br />\n裁判官花了約十分鐘重複判決原因，先宣讀D2判刑，D2代表律師在上次求情時話，<strong>D2無暴力無汽油彈，如果佢有就會被控告暴動，佢無係走運，如果因為咁嘅原因而減刑，將會係全球法律界最大笑話。</strong><br />\n<br />\n控罪(1)：量刑起點係15個月監禁，冇減刑理由<br />\n控罪(4)：量刑起點係4個月監禁，冇減刑理由<br />\n控罪(5)：同意彈藥無殺傷力，但被告行為令到催淚彈不能發揮效果，迫使警員要使用更大武力，或者埋身肉搏，增加受傷風險，量刑起點係9個月監禁，冇減刑理由<br />\n<br />\n由於考慮控罪(1)時已經有控罪(4)的元素，因此控罪(1)與控罪(4)同期執行，控罪(1)和(5)不同，酌情3個月同期執行，總刑期判監21個月。<br />\n<br />\nD1希望再入讀西廚學院，但唔可能無需面對法律制裁；老師的求情信說被告因公義而犯案，咁要反問老師為何教出一名咁嘅學生；傳道人指被告希望做廚師為社會帶來幸福，本席認為不會因為被告而社會少了幸福；被告自己表示反省，但懲教報告中顯示被告在還押期間，還認為該集結不是非法，顯示反省不是真誠。<br />\n<br />\n如果D1係成年人，<br />\n控罪(1)：量刑起點係15個月監禁<br />\n控罪(2)：量刑起點係4個月監禁<br />\n控罪(3)：量刑起點係9個月監禁，6個月分期執行<br />\n<br />\n<strong>懲教署嘅報告指適合勞教中心，懲教署人員未知被告在還押前嘅表現，在庭上胡說八道，誣告警員使用過度暴力；判入教導所培養就業機會，對被告和社會都有益處，就控罪(1), (2), (3)，判處被告入教導所。</strong><br />\n<br />\nD2 申請保釋等候上訴被拒。"},{"pid":"940945a59deaa51e6226a84afe3a5440e3281d20","tid":2489637,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8834d080a142d9bd5090ad1656eb3cae9903fa5","tid":2489637,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:20:23.000Z","msg":"點解粉嶺可以同時出到佢同蘇文隆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:24:31.000Z","msg":"仲有吳重儀呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"179b13261d0b594e935697b1aa67a3939dc0c7ec","tid":2489637,"uid":24160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc9304507a254706ed6ac7d2392873ab9a1d7f57","tid":2489637,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:09:59.000Z","msg":"網民前年11月13日發起全港三罷，兩名青年早前被裁定在大埔參與非法集結及違反蒙面法等五罪罪成，案件今早判刑。<strong><span class=\"red\">裁判官陳炳宙指案發時17歲的無業青年否認犯案，自辯時更在庭上胡說八道，誣告警員制服他時使用過份武力，可見他沒真誠反省，形容他是「讀書唔成，又冇半點一技之長嘅年輕人」，故拒絕接納報告建議判處青年入住刑期較短的勞教中心，而是將青年判入教導所。至於同案倉務員，陳官指他辯稱受社會氣氛影響而犯案並非求情理由，否則是「全球司法歷史上最大笑話」，最後判他入獄21個月。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210415/ANCSPQELLZC4NHNRBJ5WLQ33KU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210415%2FANCSPQELLZC4NHNRBJ5WLQ33KU%2F&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sJWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=decd6a52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210415%2FANCSPQELLZC4NHNRBJ5WLQ33KU%2F&h=df3e2da7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210415/ANCSPQELLZC4NHNRBJ5WLQ33KU/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:24:43.000Z","msg":"陳狗官你讀得成書 都亂屈後生仔 咁又有乜撚嘢作為呀 狗官!!"},{"pid":"87f11d06697721b2e369a4c3e5f29d0a82938133","tid":2489637,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:26:52.000Z","msg":"陳炳宙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec8877b2f868b988a83a2d2c51a7d5cd5e80abb","tid":2489637,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:29:48.000Z","msg":"重手當有公道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 軍事迷執落水袋收藏就當係整熄啲彈"},{"pid":"68f3bca464bab74c87600f250ff97f91a0d92958","tid":2489637,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0a7efaaba4c370da0fdd66792d1e663fb72237","tid":2489637,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:56:30.000Z","msg":"寸過馬撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e8505b0b727d9b2a1cce80f4c37f66086ca18f","tid":2489637,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:57:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4033a703ca4d04114c62b8b01c89258479f0df","tid":2489637,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68f3bca464bab74c87600f250ff97f91a0d92958","tid":2489637,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:58:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100be9a38691b06b769e01264f8b9a182caea946","tid":2489637,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:01:47.000Z","msg":"痴線呢件狗官<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c71d6faff947e6b0ba04c8a602694fdb74a4e0","tid":2489637,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:04:51.000Z","msg":"佢仲要分開d罪嚟判刑<br />\n即係你想上訴都減唔到幾多<br />\n<br />\n好撚惡毒"},{"pid":"f5f9d0941ab3486dbdeda2fe04807b1a0a1131e1","tid":2489637,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c0a992cba159a6c15c4d4732e5fc87f9d0b5082","tid":2489637,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:15:10.000Z","msg":"至於巢，陳官指雖然他案發時沒使用暴力，但這不可用作減刑理由，因為若果他有使用暴力，早已被控暴動等嚴重罪行。<br />\n<br />\n對於巢的母親指，他因受社會氣氛影響而犯案，陳官認為守法是個人選擇，巢選擇犯法，就要付出代價，而正正是他這樣的人，才會影響社會氣氛。陳官更直言，若因這個求情理由而獲輕判，「實在係全球司法歷史上最大笑話」。<br />\n<br />\n就非法集結及蒙面罪，巢分別被判監15個月及4個月，全數同期執行；非法管有彈藥罪則判監9個月，當中6個月須與前兩項控罪分期執行，最終總刑期為21個月。<br />\n<br />\n辯方為巢申請保釋，以等候上訴定罪的結果。但陳官認為上訴沒有合理成功機會，故拒絕申請。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:14:22.000Z","msg":"非法管有彈藥罪判9個月？？<br />\n無撚野下話"},{"pid":"a08c510dd30c1e138597389f0022c5f0be2fec78","tid":2489637,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5f9d0941ab3486dbdeda2fe04807b1a0a1131e1","tid":2489637,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c0a992cba159a6c15c4d4732e5fc87f9d0b5082","tid":2489637,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:15:10.000Z","msg":"至於巢，陳官指雖然他案發時沒使用暴力，但這不可用作減刑理由，因為若果他有使用暴力，早已被控暴動等嚴重罪行。<br />\n<br />\n對於巢的母親指，他因受社會氣氛影響而犯案，陳官認為守法是個人選擇，巢選擇犯法，就要付出代價，而正正是他這樣的人，才會影響社會氣氛。陳官更直言，若因這個求情理由而獲輕判，「實在係全球司法歷史上最大笑話」。<br />\n<br />\n就非法集結及蒙面罪，巢分別被判監15個月及4個月，全數同期執行；非法管有彈藥罪則判監9個月，當中6個月須與前兩項控罪分期執行，最終總刑期為21個月。<br />\n<br />\n辯方為巢申請保釋，以等候上訴定罪的結果。但陳官認為上訴沒有合理成功機會，故拒絕申請。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:14:22.000Z","msg":"非法管有彈藥罪判9個月？？<br />\n無撚野下話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:17:10.000Z","msg":"仲要係已經無殺傷力嘅彈藥"},{"pid":"4d5892b0b9b7af88129fe2498f4d75a0235ca0ec","tid":2489637,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:07:45.000Z","msg":"前年 11 月 13 日，網民發起第 3 日全港「三罷」，兩名青年被指在大埔參與非法集結，其後分別被搜出士巴拿、索帶及催淚煙彈小彈頭等物品，早前經審訊後被裁定全部罪成。粉嶺法院裁判官陳炳宙今（ 15 日）指，首被告自辯時在庭上胡說八道，誣告警員制服他時使用過分武力，可見他沒真誠反省，故判入教導所。至於同案倉務員，裁判官強調，被告受社會氣氛影響而犯案並非求情理由，若然因此輕判的話，相信會成為「全球司法歷史上最大笑話」，終判其入獄 21 個月，並拒絕讓他保釋等候上訴。<br />\n<br />\n辯方強調，蘇在還押期間有所反省，明白到案件嚴重性，亦深知自己令家人傷心失望，望法庭接納報告建議，判入體能要求高、相對辛勞的勞教中心，並強調這絕非輕判選項。<br />\n<br />\n惟裁判官反駁謂，報告亦指被告適合判入教導所，認為教導所的刑期較長，能反映案件嚴重性，又指蘇在西廚學院半途而廢，相信他可在教導所學一門手藝。不過，辯方並不同意「半途而廢」的說法，重申他僅因本案而被迫輟學。裁判官質疑：「咁件案未完結，佢又日日食飯、日日瞓覺，咪一樣咁做人？」辯方再回應稱，案件一日未完結，他的生活難以如常繼續。<br />\n<br />\n判刑時，裁判官參考高等法院案例指，市民行使集會權利時，必須以干擾公眾秩序之行為劃界，否則社會將變得無法無天。觀乎本案，案發時正值香港史無前例的社會運動，當日有人發動「全港大三罷」，大埔太和路有逾百人非法集結，可見必有預謀。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官續指，雖然蘇口口聲聲指會繼續學業，但不代表他毋須接受法律制裁，並引述蘇的老師求情信內容：「他因追求公義而犯案」，反問「呢位老師應該問一問自己，點解自己學生會相信犯法係追求公義嘅手法？」對於傳道人求情指，蘇希望透過廚藝為人帶來幸福，裁判官明言「相信少咗佢呢名中途輟學嘅學廚，唔會令市民少咗幸福。」<br />\n<br />\n裁判官又引述蘇親撰的求情信指，他不知道涉案集結屬違法的說法，反映其所謂的「反省」沒未點真誠，同時拒絕接納他年少無知的辯解，強調他當時看見警員便轉身逃跑，必然自知犯法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/11-13-%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94-%E5%85%A9%E7%94%B7%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E5%9B%9A-21-%E6%9C%88%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%A5%E6%95%99%E5%B0%8E%E6%89%80-%E5%AE%98-%E7%A8%B1%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%B0%A3%E6%B0%9B%E7%8A%AF%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E6%B8%9B%E5%88%91-%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E7%AC%91%E8%A9%B1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F11-13-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%2594-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%2594%25B7%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%259B%259A-21-%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B0%258E%25E6%2589%2580-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%25B0%259B%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A1%2588%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25B8%259B%25E5%2588%2591-%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%258F%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25AC%2591%25E8%25A9%25B1%2F&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sJWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=83dcd704\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F11-13-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%2594-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%2594%25B7%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%259B%259A-21-%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B0%258E%25E6%2589%2580-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%25B0%259B%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A1%2588%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25B8%259B%25E5%2588%2591-%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%258F%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25AC%2591%25E8%25A9%25B1%2F&h=158007b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/11-13-%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94-%E5%85%A9%E7%94%B7%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E5%9B%9A-21-%E6%9C%88%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%A5%E6%95%99%E5%B0%8E%E6%89%80-%E5%AE%98-%E7%A8%B1%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%B0%A3%E6%B0%9B%E7%8A%AF%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E6%B8%9B%E5%88%91-%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E7%AC%91%E8%A9%B1/</a>"},{"pid":"9da570b0ee99d87421e81e78196f53d5560a6182","tid":2489637,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:08:39.000Z","msg":"裁判官直言，在蘇否認控罪那一刻起，他已放棄了所有獲得輕判的機會，加上他在自辯時胡說八道，誣告警員制服他時使用過分武力，事後又沒有向警員道歉，但他指判監對年輕罪犯而言，是最後才會考慮的選擇。裁判官又斥，蘇作為一名「讀書唔成，又冇半點一技之長嘅年輕人」，相信比起著重體力懲罰的勞教中心，他更適合在教導所培養守法意識及謀生技能。<br />\n<br />\n至於次被告，裁判官指他雖然在案發時沒使用暴力，但不能構成減刑理由。對於他指因受社會氣氛影響而犯案，裁判官認為是他的個人選擇，選擇犯法就要付出代價，而正正是他這樣的人，才會影響社會氣氛，又指若因這個求情理由而輕判，「實在係全球司法歷史上最大笑話」，最後判囚 21 個月。<br />\n<br />\n辯方隨即為巢申請保釋，以等候就定罪上訴，惟裁判官認為，上訴沒有合理成功機會，故駁回申請。"},{"pid":"748fa128e59a6725e2900bba16996673d02b29a3","tid":2489637,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:16:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />狗眼看人低到"},{"pid":"573322b94c9e426507963393edc977551d4f1d6b","tid":2489637,"uid":275243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:23:10.000Z","msg":"狗官<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de6323696ff3007a02c4e3f33b67fdae97facd3","tid":2489637,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:55:45.000Z","msg":"香港基本法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全球司法笑話<br />\n唔排除陳炳宙先生係睇一帶一路國家法律為首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8155123f486075dbbe20a3d2031040d0d7c65c4","tid":2489637,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:59:23.000Z","msg":"上訴抽到李運騰黃祟厚應該可以減刑<br />\n彭潘就898"}]}